INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2012-07-02 04:46:11','2012-07-02 04:46:11','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2012-07-08 17:46:31','2012-07-09 00:46:31','',0,'http://sd-trunk/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2012-07-02 04:46:11','2012-07-02 04:46:11','<h3>The Early Years...</h3>\r\n<p>Alan’s business acumen began to develop from the age of 16 years when his father purchased his first business for him. His passion for business continued to grow and launched him successfully into the world of Professional and Personal Development at age 22. By the time Alan was 26 he had become an International company’s Training Facilitator for Australia, USA and Asia. In 1988 Alan at 30 years of age began his own International consulting and training company.</p>\r\n<h3>Longevity...</h3>\r\n<p>With a broad and successful background in business spanning 37 years, Alan has competently brought skilled implementation of strategies, practical facilitation techniques and advanced training programs to companies across the world. His obvious and long term experience in the business world, together with his professional level of skill, command respect and attention from corporations and place Alan’s services in high demand.</p>\r\n<h3>Business Values...</h3>\r\n<p>An uncompromising application of sound business principles and inspirational ideas combined with \'old fashion values\' has earned Alan a reputation for business excellence with integrity. Alan\'s life is dedicated to bringing significant improvement to companies and their staff. His unique \'people skill\' ability and advanced training techniques allows Alan to implement \'change for gain\'... resulting in long term measurable and significant profitability. Alan is passionately committed to delivering excellence in all areas of business life.</p>\r\n<h3>Strengths...</h3>\r\n<p>Alan is a gifted strategist, facilitator, platform speaker, educator and trainer who provides a diversity of customized services to fit the need of a company, small business or large corporation. Alan identifies, designs and implements a unique program for each company client and then competently and intentionally delivers the program... with Quantum results...!</p>','Alan Strudwick','','publish','open','open','','about','','','2012-07-12 21:43:11','2012-07-13 04:43:11','',0,'http://sd-trunk/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2012-07-08 13:01:35','2012-07-08 20:01:35','','About Us','About Us','publish','open','open','','4','','','2012-07-12 17:59:41','2012-07-13 00:59:41','',0,'http://sd-trunk/?p=4',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(6,1,'2012-07-11 22:21:05','2012-07-12 05:21:05','<h3>The Early Years...</h3>\nAlan’s business acumen began to develop from the age of 16 years when his father purchased his first business for him. His passion for business continued to grow and launched him successfully into the world of Professional and Personal Development at age 22. By the time Alan was 26 he had become an International company’s Training Facilitator for Australia, USA and Asia. In 1988 Alan at 30 years of age began his own International consulting and training company.\n<h3>Longevity...</h3>\nWith a broad and successful background in business spanning 37 years, Alan has competently brought skilled implementation of strategies, practical facilitation techniques and advanced training programs to companies across the world. His obvious and long term experience in the business world, together with his professional level of skill, command respect and attention from corporations and place Alan’s services in high demand. \n<h3>Business Values...</h3>\nAn uncompromising application of sound business principles and inspirational ideas combined with ‘old fashion values’ has earned Alan a reputation for business excellence with integrity.  Alan\'s life is dedicated to bringing significant improvement to companies and their sta