ation process is our ability to competently adapt to the training needs of every group. Our training programs, workshops and activities ensure outcomes that are inspirational, results focused, pioneering and dynamic.\r\n<h3>Motivation...</h3>\r\nQuantum Strategies acknowledges that motivation is the key to improved performance. We also know that motivation ‘practice’ and theory are areas of challenge for any business. With our understanding and appreciation of employee motivation we create ‘key’ processes from advanced, solid and practical techniques to ensure that staff remain ‘self’ motivated in their work performance.','Professional Development','','inherit','open','open','','42-revision-5','','','2012-07-12 19:32:48','2012-07-13 02:32:48','',42,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/2012/07/12/42-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(128,1,'2012-07-12 19:18:57','2012-07-13 02:18:57','<h3>Your Needs...</h3>\r\nQuantum Strategies will assist your company by providing Needs Analyses, Research Interviews, Focus Groups and Culture Change Programs. QS know the keys to develop effective organisations that align leadership, strategy and culture to forge the company ahead with change that brings significant and lasting transformation.\r\n<h3>Innovating Solutions...</h3>\r\nQuantum Strategies’ goal is to bring economically efficient solutions that meet your companies pressing current need and to also provide long term solutions. QS offers a \'partnership\' approach to understanding and interpreting your company\'s needs which in turn enables us to supply our  innovative solutions to each problem and challenge. \r\n<h3>Implementation...</h3>\r\nAfter the identification and analysis interpretation of your company\'s needs, Quantum Strategies provide the process of implementation. QS have a commitment to excellence that ensures this process offers your company ‘tried and true’ techniques that lead to positive and lasting change and dynamic outcomes for your company.','Strategic Consulting','