ifies, designs and implements a unique program for each company client and then competently and intentionally delivers the program... with Quantum results...!','Alan Strudwick','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-8','','','2012-07-11 22:21:46','2012-07-12 05:21:46','',2,'http://qs.spiraldesign.ca/2012/07/11/2-revision-8/',0,'revision','',0);
